    <item>
      <title>Scholz 联盟仍在寻求就修订后的 2024 年预算达成协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/scholz-coalition-still-seeking-agreement-on-revised-2024-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨及其在德国执政联盟的合作伙伴未能在一夜之间就修订后的 2024 年预算达成协议，并将于周三在柏林总理府继续进行谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/scholz-coalition-still-seeking-agreement-on-revised-2024-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 08:32:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在美国战争援助担忧之际，俄罗斯用无人机攻击乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/russia-hits-ukraine-with-drone-barrage-amid-us-war-aid-worries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰周三遭受十多天来最大规模的俄罗斯无人机袭击，因华盛顿援助谈判陷入僵局，美国的军事支持资金可能耗尽。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/russia-hits-ukraine-with-drone-barrage-amid-us-war-aid-worries</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 07:29:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
